# get_irida_sample_unpaired_metadata
# get single-end (unpaired) sequence file metadata for a sample. Does not download any files.
#
# PROJECT_ID is used only for tab completion to narrow down samples, not passed to the API
# SAMPLE_ID is the actual argument used in the curl call
# example: get_irida_sample_unpaired_metadata [TAB once for project id] 150:test_gmarselis [TAB for sample id] 1234:some-sample
#
# NOTE: endpoint is /api/samples/{id}/unpaired, not /api/samples/{id}/sequenceFiles/unpaired.
# /sequenceFiles/unpaired returns 500 on IRIDA 23.01.3 - routing bug, see issue #4.
